    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-08-30T16:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-08-30T16:00:00-05:00" n="838"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d838">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">840.50/2477: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Ecuador</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Scotten</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Quito</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-08-30T16:00:00-05:00"
                            >August 30, 1943—4 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received 11:30 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>759. Embassy’s 697, August 9, 6 p.m.<note n="5" xml:id="d838fn5">Not
                        printed.</note> Note from Foreign Office marked confidential states Ecuador
                    is disposed to adhere in principle to the draft agreement but proposes that the
                    following sentence be added to article VI: “This proportionate share shall be
                    fixed by taking into consideration the economic situation of each nation,
                    represented by its respective government, member of the administration of the
                    Allied Nations.”</p>
                <p>Text being forwarded to Department by today’s airmail pouch.<note n="6"
                        xml:id="d838fn6">Note dated August 28, not printed.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Scotten</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
